          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this view is medium. The SQL logic involves multiple joins across system views and tables to gather comprehensive metadata about database columns. The complexity arises from the need to correctly join and filter data from different sources, handle various data types, and concatenate strings to form fully qualified names. The use of conditional logic to format data types further adds to the complexity."
        }
